---
// src/pages/about/maryam-zafar.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Maryam Zafar | Lead Travel Editor & Saudi Arabia Specialist" 
  description="Meet Maryam Zafar, the Lead Travel Editor of Saudi Travel Hub. Discover her travel credentials, tourism experience, and FIFA 2034 insights."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.sauditravelhub.com/about/maryam-zafar/"
>
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Maryam Zafar",
    "jobTitle": "Lead Travel Editor",
    "worksFor": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Saudi Travel Hub"
    },
    "url": "https://www.sauditravelhub.com/about/maryam-zafar/",
    "sameAs": [
      "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maryamzafar-travel",
      "https://twitter.com/maryamzafar_travel"
    ],
    "description": "Expert travel editor specializing in Saudi Arabia tourism, FIFA 2034 logistics, and cultural heritage."
  }
  </script>

  <main id="main-content" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.8;">
    
    <!-- AUTHOR BREADCRUMB -->
    <nav style="font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; color: var(--white-dim);">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Home</a> &rsaquo; 
      <span style="color: var(--white-dim);">About</span> &rsaquo; 
      <span>Maryam Zafar</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- BIO SECTION -->
    <section style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div style="width: 180px; height: 180px; border-radius: 50%; overflow: hidden; border: 3px solid var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
          <img 
            src="/images/authors/maryam-zafar.jpg" 
            alt="Maryam Zafar headshot" 
            style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; background: var(--surface2);"
            onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><rect width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 fill=%22%230a1324%22/><text x=%2250%25%22 y=%2255%25%22 font-family=%22Outfit%22 font-size=%2228%22 fill=%22%23c8a96e%22 font-weight=%22700%22 text-anchor=%22middle%22>MZ</text></svg>'"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem;">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maryamzafar-travel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;" aria-label="LinkedIn Profile">
            💼
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/maryamzafar_travel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;" aria-label="Twitter Profile">
            🐦
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Lead Travel Editor</div>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;">Maryam Zafar – Lead Travel Editor &amp; Saudi Arabia Specialist</h1>
        
        <div style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--white-dim); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem;">
          <p>
            Maryam Zafar is the Founder and Lead Travel Editor of Saudi Travel Hub. With over five years of dedicated experience covering tourism and cultural development in the Middle East, she has become a leading independent voice on travel in the Gulf region. Maryam has personally traveled to all 13 provinces of Saudi Arabia, from the high altitude valleys of Asir to the historic alleys of Al-Balad in Jeddah and the ancient tombs of Hegra in AlUla.
          </p>
          <p>
            Her extensive on-the-ground research enables her to provide deep, practical insights into local customs, transit networks, and accommodation. As Saudi Arabia prepares for the historic FIFA World Cup 2034, Maryam has focused her latest efforts on analyzing stadium construction plans, fan zone layouts, and logistics corridors to create the ultimate resource for incoming international fans. Her analytical approach combined with local travel knowledge bridges the gap between tourist expectations and real-world conditions.
          </p>
          <p>
            Before launching Saudi Travel Hub, Maryam worked as a travel contributor for several prominent international publications, documenting the region's cultural renaissance. She holds a degree in Middle Eastern Studies and regularly collaborates with regional hospitality experts. When she is not writing or editing guides, she can be found exploring off-the-grid desert trails or documenting traditional Najdi recipes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CREDENTIALS & TRUST SIGNALS -->
    <section style="background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2.5rem; margin-top: 3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.75rem; color: #fff; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.75rem;">Professional Credentials &amp; Industry Trust</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; color: var(--white-dim); font-size: 1.05rem;">
        <li>
          <strong>Verified Tourism Guide Partner (No. 4022)</strong> &mdash; Partner accreditation and verification in accordance with regional Saudi Ministry of Tourism hospitality guidelines.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Featured Contributor</strong> &mdash; Published articles and insights in <em>Gulf Travel Quarterly</em> and <em>Middle East Heritage Magazine</em>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Keynote Speaker</strong> &mdash; Guest presenter at the 2025 Riyadh Tourism Innovation Forum covering the digital transformation of heritage sites.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Member of the International Travel Writers Alliance</strong> &mdash; Standard compliance with professional international travel journalism ethics.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
